Halo!
Nowadays, even if your image is a PNG without background, 
the gif produced by the online gif maker still has a white background, 
which will cause great trouble to users.

This code can be run using Google Colab(online!!), which is quick and easy!

Instructions:
1. Open https://colab.research.google.com/
2. Create a New Notebook
3. In the Files panel on the left, click File, then Upload. Upload all your grid images.
4. In a new code window, paste the following code and run it.

enjoy:)